page.title: 01PROFILE OF OUR AREA.
page.content: Our area is divided into six communities, Harraby, Upperby, Currock, Denton Holme, Carleton, and Blackwell. {Harraby}is dominated by private and council housing and there is a large industrial estate. {Upperby}is mainly private semi_detached and council estates. { Currock}is mainly private terrace housing and is an older area of Carlise. {Denton Holme}is dominated by large furnishing warehouses and D.I.Y. stores. {Carleton}is a small village and country area. { Blackwell}is dominated by the racecourse (horses) and includes private housing. { MORE DETAILED INFORMATION Page 17.
